&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PA and LNA: &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.minicircuits.com/WebStore/modelSearch.html?model=ZX60-53LNB%2B&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;ZX60-53LNB+&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
